{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-destination-page-tsx","path":"/destination/kzn_midlands/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://www.active-escapes.co.za"}},"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"/destination/kzn_midlands/"},"id":"38e29475-7752-5a7a-8416-6c45546bef60","frontmatter":{"meta":{"title":"KZN Midlands","description":"KZN Midlands"},"destinationName":"KZN Midlands","code":"kzn_midlands","banner":{"heading":"The Midlands of KwaZulu-Natal","subHeading":"Land of milk, arts and mountain biking","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.92,"src":"/static/ccf9458fd97c6b490fce0e3860704836/d8255/dest-midlands.jpg","srcSet":"/static/ccf9458fd97c6b490fce0e3860704836/9104c/dest-midlands.jpg 480w,\n/static/ccf9458fd97c6b490fce0e3860704836/a6352/dest-midlands.jpg 960w,\n/static/ccf9458fd97c6b490fce0e3860704836/d8255/dest-midlands.jpg 1920w","srcWebp":"/static/ccf9458fd97c6b490fce0e3860704836/25f09/dest-midlands.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/ccf9458fd97c6b490fce0e3860704836/61be4/dest-midlands.webp 480w,\n/static/ccf9458fd97c6b490fce0e3860704836/1fb14/dest-midlands.webp 960w,\n/static/ccf9458fd97c6b490fce0e3860704836/25f09/dest-midlands.webp 1920w","sizes":"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"}},"publicURL":"/static/ccf9458fd97c6b490fce0e3860704836/dest-midlands.jpg"}},"intro":{"heading":"Midlands Meanderings","text":["Lying comfortably at the foothills of the Drakensberg, lies a fertile strip of rolling farmlands known colloquially as the Midlands. Having the advantage of being close to the mountains and to the N3, the Midlands offers the perfect middle-distance option for people who want a short break from big city life.","The rolling green hills, clean air and quaint historical buildings make for a picturesque backdrop and provided brilliant fodder for creative minds. In the 1970's many artists and crafters settled into the Midlands permanently, and by the mid-80's were working collaboratively to exhibit and sell their work. This small co-op grew organically to become the Midlands Meander: an easy to navigate, slowly unfolding tourist route that leads from cheesery to pottery to country restaurant to microbrewery and beyond.","While the Midlands Meander is well-known for shopping and lazy lunches, these days it’s also known for its extensive mountain biking, trail-running and hiking offerings. The small town of Howick is home to a network of single-track linking to the Karkloof forests; whilst cross country jeep tracks connect across private farmland to Lotheni and in to the Kamberg."],"inset":{"bestSeason":"Jan – Dec","locations":"Howick, Karkloof, Nottingham Road, Kamberg","image":null,"icon":null},"link":null},"customListings":null}},"allHolidayTypes":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"c6f07255-e27f-532c-83ac-47d6334747e9","frontmatter":{"activityName":"Family Friendly","code":"family"}}},{"node":{"id":"d10dcb60-faa5-535f-8da4-b9ffbe5d8f80","frontmatter":{"activityName":"Groups","code":"groups"}}},{"node":{"id":"1d7762e1-c052-5884-95e9-7353c794692d","frontmatter":{"activityName":"Hiking / Slackpacking","code":"hiking"}}},{"node":{"id":"acef8b22-705d-54ca-998b-68ade8cdfb16","frontmatter":{"activityName":"Horse Riding","code":"horseriding"}}},{"node":{"id":"b23214f1-81c1-557c-9c04-178b3541cd95","frontmatter":{"activityName":"Mountain Biking","code":"mountainbiking"}}},{"node":{"id":"9bdbb2d8-4df0-5db0-87fb-0acae77edb5c","frontmatter":{"activityName":"Nature Getaway","code":"nature"}}},{"node":{"id":"fcb8189b-4966-5c9c-ad24-b2fcbe689ad5","frontmatter":{"activityName":"Rafting","code":"rafting"}}},{"node":{"id":"e8c56948-96bf-5837-9d26-0fa6e1639b80","frontmatter":{"activityName":"Retreats","code":"retreats"}}},{"node":{"id":"8488a603-22e2-5e93-95cb-b66b2b460de1","frontmatter":{"activityName":"Running","code":"running"}}}]},"allSubactivitiesTypes":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"79bddb62-5150-5dde-884c-1dffe7fd51e2","frontmatter":{"title":"Expedition","code":"expedition